ActIndian Act
SubjectAddition to Sucker Creek Indian Reserve No. 23, Ontario
PrecisOrder setting apart 0.353 hectare (0.872 acre) of land including mines and minerals for the use and benefit of the Aundeck Omni Kaning First Nation as an addition to SUCKER CREEK INDIAN RESERVE NO. 23, located in the Town of Northeastern Manitoulin and the Islands at approximately 5 kilometres from the Town of Little Current, in Ontario.
